  "body": "## Description\r\nIf you pass a too small block number to the hardhat_reset function, then when passing a valid block number to this function, an error occurs\r\n\r\n## Envinroment\r\n- macOS Monterey 12.1\r\n- node 16.13.0\r\n- hardhat 2.8.2\r\n\r\n## Steps\r\n1. setup hardhat.config.js\r\n```\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  networks: {\r\n    hardhat: {\r\n      forking: {\r\n        url: \"\"https://eth-mainnet.alchemyapi.io/v2/<id>\",\r\n        blockNumber: 13961175\r\n      },\r\n      chainId: 1\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n};\r\n```\r\n2. run `hardhat node`\r\n3. call `hardhat_reset` with invalid block number\r\n```\r\ncurl --location --request POST 'http://localhost:8545' \\\r\n--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\r\n--data-raw '{\r\n    \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n        \"method\": \"hardhat_reset\",\r\n        \"params\": [{\r\n            \"forking\": {\r\n                \"jsonRpcUrl\": \"https://eth-mainnet.alchemyapi.io/v2/<id>\",\r\n                \"blockNumber\": 1\r\n            }\r\n        }],\r\n        \"id\": 1\r\n}'\r\n```\r\ngot an error:\r\n```\r\n{\r\n    \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n    \"id\": 1,\r\n    \"error\": {\r\n        \"code\": -32603,\r\n        \"message\": \"Cannot fork mainnet from block 1.\\n\\nHardhat Network's forking functionality only works with blocks from at least spuriousDragon.\"\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n4. call `hardhat_reset` with valid block number\r\n```\r\ncurl --location --request POST 'http://localhost:8545' \\\r\n--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\r\n--data-raw '{\r\n    \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n        \"method\": \"hardhat_reset\",\r\n        \"params\": [{\r\n            \"forking\": {\r\n                \"jsonRpcUrl\": \"https://eth-mainnet.alchemyapi.io/v2/<id>\",\r\n                \"blockNumber\": 13961175\r\n            }\r\n        }],\r\n        \"id\": 1\r\n}'\r\n```\r\ngot an error:\r\n```\r\n{\r\n    \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n    \"id\": 1,\r\n    \"error\": {\r\n        \"code\": -32603,\r\n        \"message\": \"Cannot fork mainnet from block 1.\\n\\nHardhat Network's forking functionality only works with blocks from at least spuriousDragon.\"\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Results\r\n**Expected**: successful reset to 13961175 block\r\n```\r\n{\r\n    \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n    \"id\": 1,\r\n    \"result\": true\r\n}\r\n```\r\n**Got**: an error\r\n```\r\n{\r\n    \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n    \"id\": 1,\r\n    \"error\": {\r\n        \"code\": -32603,\r\n        \"message\": \"Cannot fork mainnet from block 1.\\n\\nHardhat Network's forking functionality only works with blocks from at least spuriousDragon.\"\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```",
